</div><article><div id="title"><div class="title_box"><div class=""><h1>Polio in USA, Track Record  of Victims (1916-1955) then Control with Salk and Oral Polio Vaccines</h1></div></div><div class="author_attribution">
<div class="author_byline">By conradofontanilla<br/></div>
</div></div><div s="title_box"><div class=""><h1>Polio in USA, Track Record  of Victims (1916-1955) then Control with Salk anid="hub_container"><div id="hub_main"><div class="modfloat full"><div id="mod_24128810" class="module moduleImage"><h2 class="subtitle">Dr. Jonas E. Salk, MD and his team developed the killed poliovirus vaccine</h2><div id="imgs_24128810">				<div id="img_url_8372942" class="inline_hub_image fullWidth">
					<img src="http://s1.hubimg.com/u/8372942_f520.jpg" width="520" height="599" class="full" alt=""/>
					
